this_title: The Amazing Race Australia: Australia v New Zealand Season 3
trans_title: 极速前进：澳洲版 第三季
introduction: The Amazing Race Australia 3 is the third series of The Amazing Race Australia, the Australian version of The Amazing Race. Officially titled The Amazing Race Australia v New Zealand, the race will feature ten teams of two (five from Australia and five from New Zealand), each in a pre-existing relationship, in a race around the world for a A$250,000 grand prize.
